Class Name: TypeEffectiveness

Package: (if applicable, e.g., utils)
Language: Java

Description:

The TypeEffectiveness class provides a mechanism to determine how effective one skill type is against a defending rooster type. It supports super-effective, not very effective, and neutral matchups, influencing the damage calculation in battles. This class also provides user-friendly messages to indicate effectiveness during combat.

Key Features:

Determines damage multipliers based on attack and defender types.

Supports super effective, not very effective, and neutral interactions.

Provides textual feedback to enhance player understanding of battle outcomes.

Centralizes type effectiveness rules for easier maintenance and extension.


Methods:

